db.tasks.find({}) , db.topics.find({})


Find all the company drives which appeared between 15 oct-2020 and 31-oct-2020
db.company_drives.find({drive_date:{$gte:new Date("2020-10-15"),$lt: new Date("2020-10-31")}})

